<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>JYING SHYONG INDUSTRY CO., LTD.</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/HomeStyle.css">
</head>

<body onmousemove=/HideMenu()/ oncontextmenu="return false" ondragstart="return false" onselectstart="return false"
    onselect="document.selection.empty()" oncopy="document.selection.empty()" onbeforecopy="return false"
    onmouseup="document.selection.empty()">


    <header>
        <div class="banner">
            <img src="/images/banner_img.bmp" alt="Modern bathroom with grab bars">
            <h1>JYING SHYONG INDUSTRY</h1>
            <p>Your Trusted Partner in Safety and Accessibility</p>
        </div>
    </header>


    <main>
        <section class="products" style="text-align: center">
            <h2>Our Products</h2>
            <div class="product-grid">
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/item1.bmp" alt="Grab Bar sample 1">
                    <h3>Exposed Screws Mounting</h3>
                    <p>Flange thickness: 1.8m/m to 2.0m/m</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/item2.bmp" alt="Grab Bar sample 2">
                    <h3>Exposed Screws Mounting</h3>
                    <p>Flange thickness: 2.8m/m or 4.0m/m</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/item3.bmp" alt="Grab Bar sample 3">
                    <h3>Concealed Screws Mounting</h3>
                    <p>Thickness of flange cover: 0.7m/m, base 1.8m/m to 2.0m/m</p>
                </div>
                <div class="product">
                    <img src="/images/item4.bmp" alt="Grab Bar sample 4">
                    <h3>Concealed Screws Mounting</h3>
                    <p>Thickness of flange cover: 2.8m/m, base 1.8m/m to 2.0m/m</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="history" style="text-align: center; margin-left: 50px; margin-right: 50px;">
            <h2>Our History</h2>
            <p style="text-align:justify; font-size: 18px">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Since 1999,
                our company has been at the forefront of the global market,
                specializing in providing top-quality safety grab bars to customers worldwide.
                With our 25 years experience, we have focused on delivering excellence in both product performance and
                customer service.
                With a keen eye for international trends and standards, we have developed a diverse range of grab bars
                tailored to meet the unique needs of various regions and cultures.
                Our commitment to innovation has propelled us to become a trusted partner for distributors, contractors,
                and project managers seeking reliable safety solutions. With a firm dedication to quality assurance and
                stringent manufacturing standards, we strive to ensure that every grab bar we produce meets the highest
                levels of
                durability and reliability, offering peace of mind to our valued customers across the globe.
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="contact" style="text-align: center;">
            <h2>Contact Us</h2>
            <p style="font-style:italic">Have questions or need assistance? Our team is here to help!</p>
            <form action="/submit" method="post">
                <label for="name">Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>

                <label for="email">Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>

                <label for="message">Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" cols="50" required></textarea>

                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2024 JYING SHYONG INDUSTRY CO., LTD. | All Rights Reserved</p>
